page.title: 12YOUTH CLUB
page.content: { { { Youth Club}is a place where you can go to meet your friends and is something to do.The youth club starts at six o clock but most people come around sevenish.The games you can play are darts,snooker,table-tennis and pool. Most people play table_ tennis and pool but I play football with a sponge ball. Cans of coke cost 20p.The organisers let every-one do what they want and thats good.They've got a stereo and they play records by Duran-Duran, Phil Collins, Wham, Elton John, Paul Hardcastle, Michael Jackson and Culture Club. It's 30p a week and 60p membership a year.Everyone has a great time.
